{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-11933/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-11933"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:19:33"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["close-up"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["single shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["Woman looks concerned"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11933/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-11933","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11933/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-11933"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11933/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11933/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11933/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11933/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11933/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11933/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11933/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11933/canvas/1/10c5a5bf-ea24-44e9-877a-98ffbf113047","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T14:58:54.331Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>This scene is shot at a low angle, making Cyril’s face appear very large and above the viewer. We see her almost as Reynolds sees her as she leans over his sleeping form. This emphasizes the power dynamics in the scene. Reynolds is completely incapacitated and at the mercy of Cyril and Alma, reliant on them both to care for him and to complete his work.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11933/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:61.49750415973372,106.32279534109813,271.54742096505834,185.29118136439268"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11933/canvas/1/b2cfeb25-59b8-42e4-934c-1783203ea47d","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T14:59:37.666Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>When Cyril asks if he thinks something he ate makes him ill, he says no, inadvertently pushing any possible suspicion away from poisoning. Alma’s secret, at least for now, seems protected and undetectable.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11933/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:483.1946755407654,99.134775374376,854.5757071547422,912.0798668885192"}}}]}]}]}